          "findings": [
            {
              "message": "T001 is internally inconsistent: it says the step is \"purely additive\" and that \"no existing files are modified\", but the same step also requires moving `track/review-prompts/plan-artifacts.md` into `.harness/custom/review-prompts/`. A move changes the source tree, so this step cannot satisfy both statements as written.",
              "severity": "P1",
              "file": "track/items/review-prompts-relocation-per-layer-2026-06-19/plan.md",
              "line": 12,
              "category": "contradiction"
            },
            {
              "message": "T002 is declared CI-green at the commit boundary, but T003 is where the tests that still assert the old path strings are updated. If those tests are part of `cargo make ci`, the T002 boundary is not actually passable until the T003 expectation changes land too.",
              "severity": "P1",
              "file": "track/items/review-prompts-relocation-per-layer-2026-06-19/plan.md",
              "line": 20,
              "category": "infeasibility"
