            {
              "message": "OS-01 says the broken `briefing_file` path lint is deferred per the ADR Open Questions, but its ADR reference points to D6. D6 defines `.harness/custom/` ownership and CI behavior, not the broken-path lint deferral, so the rendered spec sends readers to the wrong design rationale for this out-of-scope item.",
